{
  "info": {
    "name": "Account Posting Orchestrator",
    "_postman_id": "apo-collection-v4",
    "description": "Full API collection for the Account Posting Orchestrator service.\n\nBase URL: http://localhost:8080/api\n\n--- Naming convention ---\nPOST / PUT request bodies  → snake_case keys (Jackson SNAKE_CASE strategy)\nGET query parameters       → camelCase (Spring @ModelAttribute binding)\n\n--- Enums ---\ncredit_debit_indicator: CREDIT | DEBIT\nstatus / leg status:    PENDING | SUCCESS | FAILED\n\n--- Source names & request types (canonical from dev DB) ---\nIMX         → IMX_CBS_GL | IMX_OBPM\nRMS         → FED_RETURN | GL_RETURN | MCA_RETURN\nSTABLECOIN  → BUY_CUSTOMER_POSTNG | BUY_CUSTOMER_POSTING | ADD_ACCOUNT_HOLD | CUSTOMER_POSTING\n\n--- Target systems ---\nCBS | GL | OBPM\n\n--- Operations ---\nPOSTING | ADD_HOLD | REMOVE_HOLD",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8080/api",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "postingId",
      "value": "1",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "legId",
      "value": "1",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "configId",
      "value": "1",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Posting Config",
      "description": "Manage routing config — maps source_name + request_type to ordered target systems.\n\nNotes:\n- order_seq determines the processing order of legs\n- Cached in memory; call POST /cache/flush after changes\n- Duplicate (request_type + order_seq) returns HTTP 422",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET All Config Entries",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/account-posting/config",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "account-posting",
                "config"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Returns every row in posting_config ordered by configId."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Config by Request Type — IMX_CBS_GL",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/account-posting/config/IMX_CBS_GL",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "account-posting",
                "config",
                "IMX_CBS_GL"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Returns the ordered legs for IMX_CBS_GL: CBS (order 1) → GL (order 2).\n\nOther valid request types: IMX_OBPM | FED_RETURN | GL_RETURN | MCA_RETURN | BUY_CUSTOMER_POSTNG | BUY_CUSTOMER_POSTING | ADD_ACCOUNT_HOLD | CUSTOMER_POSTING"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Create Config Entry",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/account-posting/config",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "account-posting",
                "config"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"source_name\": \"IMX\",\n  \"request_type\": \"IMX_CBS_GL\",\n  \"target_system\": \"CBS\",\n  \"operation\": \"POSTING\",\n  \"order_seq\": 1\n}"
            },
            "description": "Add a new config routing entry.\n\nsource_name:   IMX | RMS | STABLECOIN\nrequest_type:  IMX_CBS_GL | IMX_OBPM | FED_RETURN | GL_RETURN | MCA_RETURN | BUY_CUSTOMER_POSTNG | BUY_CUSTOMER_POSTING | ADD_ACCOUNT_HOLD | CUSTOMER_POSTING\ntarget_system: CBS | GL | OBPM\noperation:     POSTING | ADD_HOLD | REMOVE_HOLD\norder_seq:     1-based integer"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "PUT Update Config Entry",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/account-posting/config/{{configId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "account-posting",
                "config",
                "{{configId}}"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"source_name\": \"IMX\",\n  \"request_type\": \"IMX_CBS_GL\",\n  \"target_system\": \"CBS\",\n  \"operation\": \"POSTING\",\n  \"order_seq\": 1\n}"
            },
            "description": "Update an existing config entry by configId. Set {{configId}} variable or replace in the URL."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "DELETE Config Entry",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/account-posting/config/{{configId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "account-posting",
                "config",
                "{{configId}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Delete a config entry by configId. Returns HTTP 204 No Content."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Flush Config Cache",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/account-posting/config/cache/flush",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "account-posting",
                "config",
                "cache",
                "flush"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Evicts the in-memory config cache so the next request reloads from DB. Returns HTTP 204 No Content."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Account Posting",
      "description": "Core posting operations — create, search, get by ID, and retry.\n\nKey behaviours:\n- POST body fields must be snake_case (Jackson SNAKE_CASE strategy)\n- GET query params are camelCase (Spring ModelAttribute binding)\n- @Valid fires before service — validation failure returns HTTP 400 without creating any DB record\n- Duplicate end_to_end_reference_id → HTTP 422\n- reason field: 'Request processed successfully' on full success, else last failed leg's error",
